https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/faq

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/about
https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/install-win10


in powershell as SU
Enable-WindowsOptionalFeature -Online -FeatureName Microsoft-Windows-Subsystem-Linux

then (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/install-manual)

Invoke-WebRequest -Uri https://aka.ms/wsl-ubuntu-1604 -OutFile Ubuntu.appx -UseBasicParsin

then

Add-AppxPackage .\Ubuntu.appx

then (https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/wsl/initialize-distro)

<<On Windows Server, you can launch your distro's launcher executable <distro>.exe from the distro installation folder.

ubuntu.exe!


INSTALL JAVA https://stackoverflow.com/questions/36478741/installing-oracle-jdk-on-windows-subsystem-for-linux)
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install default-jdk


INSTALL NEXTFLOW (https://www.nextflow.io/docs/latest/getstarted.html)

#/mnt/d/Github/MSB1015-Assignment-3/ 

